WEBVTT

00:03.681 --> 00:05.915
I... apologize.

00:05.971 --> 00:09.252
I did not wish to... injure.

00:10.752 --> 00:13.311
Have you told Rene? About the baby?

00:13.312 --> 00:15.442
I can't.
Why not?

00:15.457 --> 00:16.936
Because the baby can't be his.

00:16.937 --> 00:19.056
George must never know.

00:19.057 --> 00:23.656
The only thing you need, to make
you unbeatable, is the right wife.

00:23.657 --> 00:26.576
George is having a second chance,
and you're taking yours.

00:26.577 --> 00:28.496
I thought perhaps
I might follow suit.

00:28.497 --> 00:30.176
So you'll be leaving Ash Park.

00:30.177 --> 00:32.216
If that's what George wants.

00:32.217 --> 00:35.576
We do hope you'll do us the honour
of being Georgie's godparents.

00:35.577 --> 00:37.336
Oh, my goodness!
No, we can't.

00:37.337 --> 00:38.577
We thought that...

00:38.577 --> 00:40.056
We're Catholic.

00:40.057 --> 00:41.696
All because of James?

00:41.697 --> 00:43.857
It's not natural what he is.
It goes against God.

00:44.897 --> 00:46.417
Rene?

00:49.177 --> 00:51.056
Quick! I need help!

00:51.057 --> 00:53.977
I can't have this baby.
I don't want it.

00:53.977 --> 00:55.737
You running away from home, missy?

00:55.738 --> 00:57.377
Aunt Peg isn't well.

